	<StaticContent title='Welcome to the Course'>
		<p>
			Art history is a fascinating subject that delves into the rich and diverse
			world of artistic expression throughout human history. From the earliest
			cave paintings to the most cutting-edge contemporary art, art history
			provides a lens through which we can explore the cultural, social, and
			political contexts that have shaped the art of different eras and regions.
